# Cloudflare Pages header rules.
#
# The problem this solves: assets were served with a four hour cache, so
# returning students kept running yesterday's JavaScript after a deploy.
# These rules ask browsers to revalidate assets on each visit (a cheap
# 304 when nothing changed) while letting Cloudflare's edge still cache
# them globally. Content updates now appear immediately.

/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

/*.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
